   		 <p style="font-size: 10px;color: gray"><%= @lugogram_name %> is not expecting you to reply. Just lean back and enjoy your <a href="<%=@lugogram_url%>"><span style="font-size: 10px;color: gray">Lugogram</span></a>.
       </p>
      </div>	
   		<br/>
  </body>
</html>